						               													<description>Burto&amp;scaron;anas &amp;#196;&amp;#141;empion&amp;#196;&amp;#129;ts is a creative and educational board game for the family. A game that will expand your vocabulary and bring out even forgotten words from the depths of your mind. The aim is to create Latvian words from the most valuable syllables, thus accumulating as many points as possible.&amp;#10;On each card, there is one syllable that, when put together during the game, forms words. The rarer the syllable used, the more valuable the word is created. Each syllable has been assigned points depending on the frequency of use of syllables in Latvian. With this game you can make more than 2000 words. These include nouns, verbs, adjectives and adverbs. Words can be formed in basic forms and inflections - either. They can be both serious and a little unserious.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
